				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hi,<BR>
<BR>
Got this item awhile back and to say it is a RARE drop is misleading. I think that SUPER-RARE is more like it. I assisted a guild member in retrieving this item and we got it on the first try so i figure &quot;heck ill stay around and get they guy again.&quot;  Well the next spawn was 3 1/2 hours later.  I waited for 2 spawns and each time got nothing. The following week was busy in real life so i figured I would camp my 50 necro down there logging on every 3 hours and trying my luck.  This proved to be tedious, each time i logged on (camped in hall outside room) i buffed up, summoned pet, and then proceeded to clear the hallway (2 gnolls one of which was a healer). after this I started on the room pulling one at a time and usually just in time to have it cleared when Rosch showed up.  After killing him a few times in this mannor i became obsessed :).  I set the alarm clock every 3 hrs and log on day and night to get this item. In the end I got the tome, 2 bubs of XP,and died twice (it can get tricky). Oh..did i mention that it took 18 spawn cycles!? You do the math, 1 spawn every 3 1/2 hrs and took me 18 spawns. Important to note. I killed every spawn in that time frame, everytime i logged on Rosh appeared 3 1/2 hrs after the previous killing, so no one capped him and got the tome while i was away. Who's not to say that the drop is random but i talked to a few ppl who have tried to get this item and many have given up after similar experiences. 
